raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "django-bootstrap-form" %}
{% set version = "3.4" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.org/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/django-bootstrap-form-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: de3f7893e515352834d446c441c0cb861637f92cebbe59d8229469c6cd3dc640

build:
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv --no-deps --no-build-isolation
  number: 1

requirements:
  host:
    - python {{ python_min }}
    - pip
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python >={{ python_min }}
    - django >=1.5
    - setuptools

test:
  imports:
    - bootstrapform
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip
    - python {{ python_min }}

about:
  home: http://github.com/tzangms/django-bootstrap-form
  summary: django-bootstrap-form
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - rxm7706
